node.text: I’ve never flown a drone before in my years of filming and that all changed when @djiglobal reached out to me to test their new product the “#DJImini2”. Legit was the most fun and easiest thing I’ve ever used to shoot.. @christian_habberstad & myself had endless creative abilities with this one 🥳.. Much love @djiglobal nobody can compete with your guys design!!

node.text: Say you spent the rest of your life alone in nature; with just yourself, who would you find first? ..”you” or “god”? 💭

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jay Alvarrez ♾ in Joshua Tree, California with @grahamnation, @illtakeyouto, @carolinejayna, and @poppyamerica. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Shooting in the desert with such a beautiful being & one of my best friends behind the camera.. that’s a vibeeee  @poppyamerica (being released in august) Love the clothing and message 🔥🤍

node.text:
Another Lap around the Sun today!! Most healthy & alive to date .. ⚡️
Thankful for every breath; each as heaven.. Love my real ones in this life!! Thank you so much for all the love, melts my fking heart!!!! ♋️🤍🇬🇷
